# Use rem via Tailwind config

- **Define dimensions in rem in `tailwind.config.js`** (under `theme.extend`) so values live in one place.
- **Use those theme classes in components** instead of arbitrary values like `h-[4rem]`.
- When adding new rem-based values, add them to the config first, then use the generated class names.
